cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and connection establishment rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_name to an invalid string 'invalid_name' will cause configuration validation failure and prevent proper gNB naming.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_name 設定為無效的字串 'invalid_name' 會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止正確的 gNB 命名。
